{"title":"春歌二首","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":2,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春歌二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家门框贴红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———春到山寨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春在日边生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春从心头来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐不尽喜悦，憧憬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写到纸上，贴到门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请月光抚摩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请日光照晒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作三月的花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮澎湃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作八月的丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋深似海……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似玉屑漫天飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似盐粒遍地撒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似千里白云铺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似万顷棉桃炸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张白纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无际无涯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请春风来描，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请红日来画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描一个东风无处不妖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画一个黄金有价春无"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似花非花胜于花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落人间百姓家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}